ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v26.group

Class RSP_Z82_COMMON_ORDER

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractStructure
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractGroup
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v26.group.RSP_Z82_COMMON_ORDER
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Group, Structure, Visitable, Serializable

    public class RSP_Z82_COMMON_ORDER
extends AbstractGroup

    Represents a RSP_Z82_COMMON_ORDER group structure (a Group object). A Group is an ordered collection of message segments that can repeat together or be optionally in/excluded together. This Group contains the following elements:

    • 1: ORC (Common Order)
    • 2: RSP_Z82_TIMING (a Group object) optional repeating
    • 3: RSP_Z82_ORDER_DETAIL (a Group object) optional
    • 4: RSP_Z82_ENCODED_ORDER (a Group object) optional
    • 5: RXD (Pharmacy/Treatment Dispense)
    • 6: RXR (Pharmacy/Treatment Route) repeating
    • 7: RXC (Pharmacy/Treatment Component Order) optional repeating
    • 8: RSP_Z82_OBSERVATION (a Group object) repeating
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
